      <title>Dish 在有争议的资产转让后启动债务互换</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/dish-parent-echostar-offers-debt-exchange-after-asset-transfer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Dish Network Corp. 的母公司在释放其部分最有价值的资产两天后，发起了一项以约 49 亿美元的可转换债务换取新债券的要约，这一颇具争议的举措激怒了许多债券持有人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/dish-parent-echostar-offers-debt-exchange-after-asset-transfer</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 02:58:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
